@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bhyott(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.59) + wp.exp((v1 + 0.45 / v1 + 0.17)))
    tmp = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.51 / v1 + 0.76) + (v2 + 0.74 / v1 + 0.76)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.78 / v2 + 0.65)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.03 / tmp + 0.39)))
    tmp = 0.11
    data[tid] = v0
